reviews.review_text: great sounding aud of a classic show perhaps the best show of the year? regardless, this is a very good audience source, the music is very present, low/ acceptable audience level...this show is blessed with excellent sounding sbd and aud recordings...best Tennessee Jed for what it's worth...first set is fantastic, very tight...second set features a nice Playin and Crazy Fingers...very well played show for the time period...
